ravel%20beneath%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMayer%20Mizrachi%2C%20the%2038-year-old%20mayor%20of%20Panama%20City%2C%20wants%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20build%20him%20a%20pedestrian%20tunnel%20under%20the%20Panama%20Canal.%20And%20Musk's%20Boring%20Company%20recently%20announced%20it%20just%20might.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPanama%20City%20this%20week%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fboringcompany%2Fstatus%2F2028694252574626163%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20named%20one%20of%2016%20finalists%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20only%20one%20outside%20the%20United%20States%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20company's%20Tunnel%20Vision%20challenge%2C%20which%20offers%20the%20winning%20municipality%20a%20free%20tunnel%20that%20can%20be%20used%20for%20freight%2C%20pedestrians%2C%20water%2C%20utilities%20or%20Loop%20%E2%80%94%20the%20electric%2C%20underground%20system%20that%20uses%20Tesla%20vehicles%20to%20transport%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMizrachi's%20idea%20is%20a%200.6%20mile%20pedestrian%20tunnel%20under%20the%20Panama%20Canal%2C%20which%20would%20give%20city%20residents%20a%20chance%20to%20%26quot%3Blive%26quot%3B%20its%20history%20and%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20vital%20maritime%20trade%20route%20that%20is%20critical%20to%20the%20global%20economy.%20More%20recently%2C%20the%20canal%20has%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20geopolitical%20tensions%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-threatens-retake-panama-canal-blasts-rip-off-fees-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20threatened%20to%20take%20control%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20waterway%20because%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20US%20was%20being%20ripped%20off%20by%20high%20fees%20and%20that%20it%20had%20come%20under%20Chinese%20influence.%20In%20February%202025%2C%20Panama%20withdrew%20from%20China's%20Belt%20and%20Road%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20winner%20will%20be%20announced%20on%20March%2023.%20Of%20the%2016%20finalists%2C%20half%20were%20in%20Tennessee%20or%20Texas%2C%20where%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-the-boring-company%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBoring%20Company%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20headquartered%20and%20where%20Mizrachi%20recently%20went%20to%20make%20his%20pitch.%20The%20project%2C%20if%20chosen%2C%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20tie%20together%20Mizrachi%2C%20the%20former%20DOGE%20leader%2C%20and%20the%20Panama%20Canal%20that%20Trump%20once%20fixated%20on%20seizing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMizrachi%2C%20the%20youngest%20mayor%20in%20the%20city's%20history%2C%20founded%20Criptext%2C%20a%20secure%20email%20platform%2C%20and%2C%20like%20Trump%2C%20has%20styled%20himself%20as%20an%20outsider.%20Like%20Musk%2C%20he%20came%20to%20office%20looking%20to%20cut%20government%20in%20the%20name%20of%20efficiency%20and%20insists%20he%20has%20succeeded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20POLITICO%2C%20which%20is%2C%20along%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Axel%20Springer%20Global%20Reporters%20Network%2C%20Mizrachi%20said%20the%20tunnel%20proposal%20began%20as%20a%20last-minute%20response%20to%20a%20Boring%20Company%20social%20media%20post%20and%20ballooned%20from%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20interview%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20did%20the%20tunnel%20idea%20begin%2C%20and%20what%20exactly%20was%20your%20pitch%20to%20The%20Boring%20Company%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMizrachi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20merely%20just%20ran%20into%20a%20tweet%20by%20the%20Boring%20Company%20in%20January%2C%20and%20they%20had%20this%20tunnel%20vision%20challenge%2C%20and%20they%20were%20offering%20a%20free%20tunnel%20up%20to%20a%20mile%20long%20anywhere%20around%20the%20world%20to%20the%20best%20idea.%20I%20did%20a%20visit%20in%20January%20to%20the%20existing%20tunnel%20that's%20being%20built%20for%20a%20subway%20station%20in%20Panama%20City%2C%20and%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20we%20built%20a%20pedestrian%20tunnel%20crossing%20the%20canal%20with%20parks%20on%20either%20side%3F%20You%20can%20tell%20the%20story%20of%20how%20the%20canal%20was%20built%20and%20the%20history%20of%20the%20country%2C%20and%20the%20biodiversity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECity%20planners%20started%20working%20on%20a%20proposal%2C%20and%20they%20kind%20of%20really%20brought%20the%20plane%20in%20for%20a%20landing%20with%20a%20beautiful%20proposal%2C%20and%20we%20submitted%20that%20on%20the%20last%20minute%20of%20the%20last%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20did%20you%20learn%20in%20Texas%20about%20how%20The%20Boring%20Company%20would%20approach%20this%20project%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMizrachi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20met%20with%20Jim%20Fitzgerald%2C%20the%20VP%20for%20global%2C%20and%20we%20kind%20of%20took%20a%20101%20on%20how%20a%20Boring%20Company%20project%20works.%20Tunnels%20are%20freaking%20expensive.%20But%20it%20turns%20out%20that%20the%20way%20that%20they%20do%20it%20makes%20it%20actually%20feasible%2C%20and%20it's%20quite%20a%20wonder%20the%20way%20that%20they%20have%20put%20this%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20I%20told%20Jim%2C%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BListen%2C%20I%20know%20this%20is%20very%20preliminary%2C%20and%20here%20are%20many%20other%20projects%20that%20they're%20considering%2C%20but%20you%20know%2C%20it%20would%20be%20quite%20a%20marvel%20that%20100%20years%20ago%2C%20you%20know%2C%20the%20US%20built%20the%20canal%2C%20and%20then%20100%20years%20later%2C%20that%20they%20would%20build%20a%20tunnel%20that%20crosses%20the%20canal%20in%20a%20modern%20marvel%20of%20engineering%20in%20the%20way%20that%20they%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20reuse%20their%20tunneling%20machines.%20Whereas%20typically%2C%20the%20tunneling%20machines%20are%20built%20specifically%20for%20a%20given%20project%2C%20and%20then%20they%20get%20buried%20with%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223992%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Boring%20Company's%20headquarters%20in%20Texas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab6e121fb3fcb426491c60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222657%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Boring%20Company's%20headquarters%20in%20Texas.%3Cp%3EBrandon%20Bell%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20would%20this%20tunnel%20mean%20for%20Panama%2C%20especially%20at%20a%20moment%20when%20the%20canal%20is%20caught%20up%20in%20broader%20geopolitical%20tensions%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMizrachi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20First%20of%20all%2C%20Panamanians%2C%20we're%20really%20proud%20of%20the%20canal%2C%20its%20management%2C%20its%20history%2C%20but%20we%20seldom%20get%20to%20live%20it.%20So%20it's%20like%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20uses%20the%20canal.%20But%20you%20know%2C%20Panamanians%2C%20we%20don't%20live%20the%20canal.%20You%20could%20go%20to%20the%20Miraflores%20Locks%2C%20and%20you%20go%20to%20the%20tourist%20center.%20You%20can%20maybe%20see%20a%20ship%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20really%20live%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20vision%20here%20is%20you%20create%20a%20public%20space%20where%20you%20integrate%20families%2C%20tourists%2C%20and%20they%20can%20cross%20the%20canal%20themselves%20with%20an%20underground%20tunnel%20that's%200.6%20miles%2C%20the%20distance.%20It's%20quite%20short%2C%20and%20I%20can%20only%20imagine%20it%20being%20almost%20an%20educational%20experience%2C%20where%20you%20can%20have%20screens%2C%20very%20thin%20screens%2C%20because%20the%20space%20is%20not%20that%20big%2C%20but%20thin%20screens%20that%20are%20showing%20the%20story%2C%20the%20history%20of%20how%20the%20canal%20was%20built%2C%20the%20biodiversity%20of%20Panama%2C%20and%20then%20stats%20on%20the%20canal%2C%20the%20impact%20that%20it%20has%20on%20world%20trade%2C%20etc.%20It%20started%20as%20an%20idea%2C%20but%20it's%20shaping%20up.%20And%20I%20think%20it%20goes%20above%20my%20pay%20grade.%20I%20spoke%20to%20the%20president%20%5Bof%20Panama%5D%20about%20this.%20This%20needs%20to%20be%20handled%20by%20a%20task%20force%20designated%20by%20the%20president%20in%20representation%20with%20the%20entire%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20do%20you%20think%20Panama%20City%20could%20beat%20out%20American%20cities%20for%20this%20project%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMizrachi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWell%2C%20there's%20one%20very%20unique%20thing%20about%20this.%20They%20don't%20have%20a%20canal.%20The%20Boring%20Company%20has%20never%20bored%20underwater%2C%20much%20less%20crossing%20a%20canal.%20And%20I%20think%20it's%20part%20of%20the%20value%20proposition%20to%20show%20themselves%20as%20engineers%2C%20how%20far%20they%20can%20go%20with%20their%20mindset%2C%20with%20their%20methodology%20and%20their%20ingenuity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20it's%20a%20pedestrian%20tunnel.%20So%20it's%20not%20a%20loop%20tunnel%20that%20is%20managed%20and%20operated%20by%20the%20Boring%20Company.%20So%20if%20you%20think%20of%20Vegas%2C%20they%20operate%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-boring-company-las-vegas-loop-tunnel-first-look-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELoop%3C%2Fa%3E%20itself.%20So%2C%20here%2C%20it's%20a%20lot%20more%20hands%20off.%20They%20build%20a%20tunnel%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20have%20an%20active%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Boring%20Company's%20Loop%20in%20Las%20Vegas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab6d1afd4fbd083f29b743%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Boring%20Company-built%20tunnel%20at%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20Convention%20Center.%3Cp%3EAaronP%2FBauer-Griffin%2FGC%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou've%20drawn%20comparisons%20between%20your%20work%20and%20DOGE-style%20cost%20cutting%20in%20Washington.%20How%20do%20you%20describe%20your%20governing%20approach%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMizrachi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20mean%2C%20honestly%2C%20I%20still%20consider%20myself%20an%20outsider.%20I%20am%20not%20subscribed%20to%20any%20political%20party%2C%20and%20I%20still%20very%20much%20employ%20the%20mindset%20of%20the%20tech%20entrepreneurial%20efficiency%20and%20try%20things%20before%20you%20scale%20things%2C%20which%20is%20uncommon%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20I%20came%20into%20office%20in%20July%202024%2C%20I%20realized%20people's%20money%20was%20being%20wasted%20on%20a%20scale%20that%20I%20was%20just%20shocked%20to%20see.%20So%20we%20were%20able%20to%20reduce%20the%20size%20of%20City%20Hall%20personnel%20by%2050%25%20so%20it%20used%20to%20have%206%2C500%20people.%20We%20reduced%20it%20to%20about%203%2C500%20people.%20And%20by%20all%20counts%2C%20City%20Hall%20is%20operating%20faster%20and%20better%20with%20more%20impact%2C%20tangible%2C%20visible%20impact%2C%20with%20less%20people.%20And%20also%2C%20we%20reduced%20the%20budget%20by%20about%2032%25%2C%20so%20we%20did%20the%20biggest%20budget%20reduction%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20city%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20originally%20ran%20in%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnewsletters%2Fwest-wing-playbook-remaking-government%2F2026%2F03%2F06%2Fpanama-city-has-a-pitch-for-elon-musk-00817532%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EPOLITICO's%20West%20Wing%20Playbook%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20appears%20on%20Business%20Insider%20through%20the%20Axel%20Springer%20Global%20Reporters%20Network.%20The%20network%20publishes%20major%20stories%20from%20the%20Axel%20Springer%20network%20of%20publications%2C%20a%20worldwide%20group%20of%20news%20