e%20G5%2C%20and%20its%20advanced%20capabilities%20make%20it%20a%20top%20pick%20for%20home%20theater%20enthusiasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20G6%20uses%20LG's%20newest%20Tandem%20OLED%20panel%2C%20which%20the%20company%20says%20delivers%20about%20a%2020%25%20bump%20in%20brightness%20over%20the%20G5.%20It%20also%20adds%20an%20upgraded%20polarizer%20filter%20to%20reduce%20reflections%20and%20glare%20without%20sacrificing%20a%20glossy%20screen.%20Seeing%20it%20in%20person%2C%20both%20upgrades%20were%20obvious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESide%20by%20side%20with%20the%20G5%2C%20the%20G6%20pushed%20brighter%2C%20more%20detailed%20highlights%2C%20giving%20HDR%20scenes%20more%20punch%20and%20a%20look%20that%20felt%20closer%20to%20what%20filmmakers%20intend.%20With%20the%20lights%20on%2C%20reflections%20on%20the%20G6%20were%20also%20more%20subdued%20than%20on%20the%20G5.%20The%20G6%20still%20isn't%20quite%20as%20glare-resistant%20as%20a%20matte%20screen%20OLED%20like%20Samsung's%20S95F%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20trade-off%3A%20matte%20panels%20can%20make%20black%20levels%20look%20hazy.%20The%20G6%20keeps%20OLEDs'%20deep%20black%20levels%2C%20even%20in%20a%20bright%20room%2C%20which%20is%20a%20big%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20got%20a%20look%20at%20what%20the%20new%20Alpha%2011%20AI%20Processor%20Gen3%20can%20do.%20LG%20played%20a%20clip%20from%20the%20movie%20%26quot%3BThe%20Green%20Knight%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20particularly%20tricky%20for%20many%20TVs%20to%20display%20properly.%20The%20dark%20scene%20features%20the%20main%20character%20diving%20into%20murky%20water%20under%20intense%20red%20lighting.%20The%20G5%20had%20issues%20here%2C%20with%20visible%20color%20banding%20and%20flickering%20shadows.%20The%20G6%20wasn't%20flawless%2C%20but%20it%20handled%20the%20scene%20much%20more%20smoothly%20and%20naturally.%20Since%20banding%20was%20one%20of%20the%20G5's%20few%20weaknesses%2C%20this%20is%20a%20meaningful%20improvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20these%20are%20the%20kinds%20of%