li%3E%3Cli%3EEmil%20Michael%2C%20the%20Pentagon's%20R%26amp%3BD%20chief%2C%20said%20it%20was%20scary%20how%20much%20power%20Anthropic%20wielded.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pentagon's%20R%26amp%3BD%20chief%20said%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20was%20%26quot%3Bscared%26quot%3B%20about%20Anthropic%20shutting%20off%20access%20to%20its%20AI%20during%20a%20critical%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20appearance%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BAll-In%20Podcast%26quot%3B%20posted%20on%20Friday%2C%20Undersecretary%20of%20Defense%20for%20Research%20and%20Engineering%20Emil%20Michael%20detailed%20two%20pivotal%20moments%20that%20culminated%20in%20the%20Pentagon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ceo-dario-amodei-pentagon-lawsuit-conversations-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eformally%20designating%20Anthropic%20as%20a%20supply%20chain%20risk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20effectively%20blacklisting%20one%20of%20the%20nation's%20largest%20AI%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20instances%2C%20Michael%20said%2C%20was%20when%20Anthropic%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdario-amodei%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDario%20Amodei%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggested%20that%20the%20impasse%20over%20how%20the%20Pentagon%20could%20deploy%20the%20AI%20startup's%20models%20could%20be%20bridged%20with%20a%20phone%20call%2C%20even%20if%20it%20came%20during%20%26quot%3Ba%20decisive%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20giving%20these%20scenarios%2C%20these%20Golden%20Dome%20scenarios%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20said%20on%20%26quot%3BAll-In%20Podcast%2C%26quot%3B%20describing%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20signature%20missile%20defense%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FgzwRflcLPAA%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Inside%20the%20Iran%20War%20and%20the%20Pentagon's%20Feud%20with%20Anthropic%20with%20Under%20Secretary%20of%20War%20Emil%20Michael%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20he's%20like%2C%20'Just%20call%20me%20if%20you%20need%20another%20exception.'%20And%20I'm%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20what%20if%20the%20balloon's%20going%20up%20at%20that%20moment%20and%20it's%20like%20a%20decisive%20action%20we%20have%20to%20take%3F%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20call%20you%20to%20do%20something.%20It's%20not%20rational.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20entirely%20clear%20what%20Anthropic%20would%20object%20to%20in%20the%20hypothetical%20Michael%20said%20he%20posed%2C%20though%20the%20implication%20is%20that%20some%20Golden%20Dome%20systems%20could%20have%20autonomous%20modes%20that%20fire%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20current%20US%20missile%20defense%20system%2C%20AI's%20role%20is%20to%20provide%20rapid%20situational%20awareness%20and%20recommendations%20for%20human%20operators.%20AI%20could%20rapidly%20assess%20whether%20a%20detected%20launch%20poses%20a%20threat%20and%20recommend%20weapons%20to%20destroy%20it.%20Decisions%20on%20whether%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20recommendations%20are%20then%20made%20by%20air%20defense%20commanders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElsewhere%20in%20the%20interview%2C%20Michael%20said%20that%20part%20of%20the%20impasse%20with%20Anthropic%20is%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bcan't%20predict%20for%20the%20next%2020%20years%20what%20all%20the%20things%20we%20might%20use%20AI%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%2C%20who%20was%20previously%20a%20top%20executive%20at%20Uber%2C%20said%20the%20department's%20concerns%20about%20Anthropic%20began%20to%20escalate%20after%20the%20US%20conducted%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-we-know-us-assault-raid-on-venezuela-capture-maduro-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20targeted%20raid%20on%20Venezuela%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20capture%20Venezuelan%20President%20Nicol%C3%A1s%20Maduro.%20The%20assault%20raised%20major%20questions%20about%20sovereignty%2C%20and%20congressional%20democrats%20questioned%20the%20decision%20not%20to%20seek%20approval%20for%20the%20deployment%20of%20US%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20raid%2C%20Michael%20said%20that%20an%20unnamed%20Anthropic%20executive%20called%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalantir-former-employees-return-shire-lord-of-the-rings-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPalantir%3C%2Fa%3E%20executive%20to%20ask%20whether%20Anthropic's%20AI%20models%20had%20been%20used%20to%20carry%20it%20out.%20The%20Pentagon%20accesses%20Anthropic's%20AI%20models%20through%20a%20government%20cloud%20that%20is%20operated%20by%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%20and%20then%20run%20by%20Palantir%2C%20Michael%20said.%20(On%20February%2027%2C%20President%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20ordered%20federal%20agencies%20to%20stop%20using%20Anthropic's%20AI%2C%20though%20that%20directive%20came%20with%20a%20six-month%20phase-out%20period.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20said%20Palantir%20officials%20were%20so%20alarmed%20by%20Anthropic's%20questions%20that%20they%20alerted%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20like%2C%20'Holy%20shit%2C%20what%20if%20this%20software%20went%20down%2C%20some%20guardrail%20kicked%20up%2C%20some%20refusal%20happened%20for%20the%20next%20fight%20like%20this%20one%2C%20and%20we%20left%20our%20people%20at%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20said%2C%20alluding%20to%20the%20US's%20current%20war%20against%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20talks%20grew%20heated%2C%20Michael%20said%20he%20felt%20like%20Anthropic%20turned%20the%20discussion%20%26quot%3Binto%20a%20PR%20game%26quot%3B%20by%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdario-amodei-pentagon-free-speech-patriots-american-values-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20publicly%20raising%20concerns%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20how%20the%20terms%20the%20Pentagon%20sought%20would%20not%20adequately%20account%20for%20potential%20misuse.%20Amodei%20has%20confirmed%20that%20Anthropic%20was%20particularly%20worried%20about%20the%20risks%20posed%20by%20fully%20autonomous%20weapons%20and%20how%20powerful%20AI%20models%20could%20be%20abused%20to%20spy%20on%20American%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20heated%20back-and-forth%2C%20Michael%20publicly%20called%20Amodei%20a%20%26quot%3Bliar%26quot%3B%20with%20%26quot%3Ba%20God-complex.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20said%20it%20formally%20notified%20Anthropic%20that%20it%20was%20declaring%20the%20company%20and%20its%20products%20to%20be%20a%20supply%20chain%20risk%2C%20the%20first%20time%20in%20history%20that%20label%20had%20been%20applied%20to%20a%20US%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmodei%20responded%20that%20his%20AI%20startup%20had%20%26quot%3Bproductive%20conversations%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20Pentagon%20in%20recent%20days%2C%20but%20Michael%20later%20said%20that%20no%20discussions%20were%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20has%20suggested%20it%20will%20challenge%20the%20designation%20in%20court%2C%20especially%20since%20Defense%20Secretary%20Pete%20Hegseth%20has%20said%20it%20prevents%20any%20defense%20contractor%20from%20doing%20business%20with%20Anthropic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20why%20the%20Pentagon%20went%20so%20far%2C%20Michael%20said%20the%20designation%20was%20not%20%26quot%3Bpunitive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20their%20model%20has%20this%20policy%20bias%2C%20let's%20call%20it%2C%20based%20on%20their%20constitution%2C%20their%20culture%2C%20their%20people%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20Lockheed%20Martin%20using%20their%20model%20to%20design%20weapons%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20a%20Lockheed%20spokesperson%20said%20it%20would%20follow%20Trump%20and%20the%20Pentagon's%20direction%20on%20whether%20it%20would%20continue%20to%20use%20Anthropic's%20products.%20Michael%20also%20called%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fba-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBoeing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20describing%20how%20the%20airplane%20manufacturer%20could%20use%20Anthropic's%20AI%20for%20non-defense%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20Boeing%20wants%20to%20use%20Anthropic%20to%20build%20commercial%20jets%20%E2%80%94%20have%20at%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBoeing%20wants%20to%20use%20it%20to%20build%20fighter%20jets.%20I%20can't%20have%20that%20because%20I%20don't%20trust%20what%20the%20outputs%20may%20be%2C%20because%20they're%20so%20wedded%20to%20their%20own%20policy%20preferences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Michael%20was%20critical%20of%20Anthropic%2C%20he%20praised%20xAI%20and%20Elon%20Musk%20for%20agreeing%20to%20the%20department's%20terms%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20deploy%20AI%20%26quot%3Bfor%20all%20lawful%20uses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20also%20praised%20OpenAI%20and%20its%20CEO%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20working%20with%20the%20Pentagon%20to%20quickly%20stand%20up%20another%20AI%20system%20capable%20of%20operating%20in%20classified%20settings%2C%20so%20the%20department%20can%20phase%20out%20Anthropic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20and%20OpenAI%20have%20received%20significant%20blowback%20online%20for%20agreeing%20to%20work%20with%20the%20Pentagon.%20Altman%20publicly%20urged%20the%20department%20not%20to%20label%20Anthropic%20a%20supply%20chain%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20his%20credit%2C%20I%20called%20him%20and%20said%2C%20'I%20need%20a%20solution%20if%20this%20thing%20goes%20sideways.%20I%20need%20multiple%20solutions.%20I'd%20like%20you%20to%20be%20one%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20he's%20like%2C%20'Okay%2C%20well%2C%20what%20can%20I%20do%20for%20the%20country%3F'%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'I%20need%20to%20get%20you%20up%20running%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20can.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpentagon-official-details-how-talks-with-anthropic-fell-apart-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772831949000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab35fd1fb3fcb4264916b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpentagon-official-details-how-talks-with-anthropic-fell-apart-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pentagon%20R%26amp%3BD%20chief%20Emil%20Michael%20said%20comments%20Anthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%20made%20during%20a%20meeting%20at%20the%20Pentagon%20set%20off%20alarm%20bells.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpentagon-official-details-how-talks-with-anthropic-fell-apart-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Canal%2B%20Shutters%20Showmax%2C%20Is%20the%20Dream%20for%20Cutting-Edge%20African%20Content%20Over%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772831947000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236681309%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Africa%E2%80%99s%20creatives%20and%20content%20producers%20are%20upset%2C%20fearful%20for%20the%20future%20and%20extremely%20concerned%20about%20where%20it%20will%20leave%20the%20continent%E2%80%99s%20film%20and%20TV%20sector%20after%20Canal%2B%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20pulling%20the%20plug%20on%20MultiChoice%E2%80%99s%20video%20stre