ia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwho-is-asif-merchant-pakistani-man-on-trial-says-iran-forced-him-in-alleged-trump-assassination-plot%2Famp_articleshow%2F129177901.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boos%20and%20boycotts%20as%20Russian%20flag%20returns%20to%20global%20sporting%20stage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772831100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F26%2F03%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-russia-paralympics_7184553.jpg%3F20260306203827%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fboos-and-boycotts-as-russian-flag-returns-to-sporting-stage-at-winter-paralympics-13516285%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Russian%20flag%20has%20returned%20to%20the%20global%20sporting%20stage%2C%20appearing%20at%20the%20Winter%20Paralympics%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20over%20a%20decade.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fboos-and-boycotts-as-russian-flag-returns-to-sporting-stage-at-winter-paralympics-13516285%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Big%20Tech%20data%20centers%20become%20a%20military%20target%20during%20the%20war%20in%20Iran%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dubai%20data%20center%20strikes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab18f3fd4fbd083f29ad43%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223206%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJebel%20Ali%20port%20was%20also%20hit%20during%20an%20Iranian%20attack.%3Cp%3ERaghed%20Waked%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDrones%20struck%20three%20Amazon%20data%20centers%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20during%20the%20war%20in%20Iran%2C%20causing%20outages.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIran's%20state%20media%20said%20the%20attacks%20were%20deliberate%2C%20underscoring%20a%20new%20reality%20of%20war.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EData%20centers%20have%20become%20the%20new%20critical%20infrastructure%20for%20the%20global%20economy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ceo-dario-amodei-pentagon-lawsuit-conversations-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic%20and%20the%20Pentagon%3C%2Fa%3E%20clashed%20over%20how%20the%20military%20should%20use%20AI%2C%20another%20new%20reality%20of%20warfare%20emerged%20several%20thousand%20miles%20away%3A%20data%20centers%20are%20now%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20Amazon%20said%20that%20three%20of%20its%20data%20centers%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20%E2%80%94%20two%20in%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20and%20one%20in%20Bahrain%20%E2%80%94%20had%20been%20damaged%20by%20drone%20strikes%20during%20the%20US-Iran%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-data-centers-middle-east-drone-strukes-us-iran-conflict-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Web%20Services%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20its%20cloud%20division%2C%20evacuated%20staff%20and%20closed%20access%20to%20at%20least%20one%20data%20center%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bstructural%20damage%26quot%3B%20and%20flooding%20caused%20by%20the%20Sunday%20attacks%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20document%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20UAE%20data%20centers%20were%20%26quot%3Bdirectly%20struck%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20the%20Bahrain%20site%20was%20damaged%20by%20a%20drone%20strike%20%26quot%3Bin%20close%20proximity%2C%26quot%3B%20Amazon%20said%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Iran's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsatellite-images-destruction-iran-drone-bases-naval-facilities-radars-stations-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIslamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20responsibility%20for%20strategically%20targeting%20one%20of%20the%20Amazon%20sites%20due%20to%20the%20company's%20support%20for%20the%20US%20military%20activities%2C%20Iran's%20state%20media%20said.%20Business%20Insider%20could%20not%20independently%20verify%20this%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Big%20Tech%20data%20centers%20have%20been%20directly%20targeted%20by%20military%20strikes%2C%20and%20it%20brings%20a%20new%20threat%20to%20the%20doorstep%20of%20companies%20that%20have%20invested%20heavily%20in%20the%20region%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20the%20AI%20boom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Middle%20East%20has%20around%204.5%20gigawatts%20of%20data%20center%20capacity%2C%20with%20an%20additional%201.7%20GW%20in%20the%20pipeline%2C%20DC%20Byte%2C%20a%20data%20center%20intelligence%20company%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Most%20of%20the%20planned%20capacity%20right%20now%20is%20for%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20the%20UAE%2C%20the%20firm%20added.%201%20GW%20is%20roughly%20equivalent%20to%20the%20power%20needed%20to%20run%20the%20homes%20of%20a%20midsize%20city%20like%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IRGC%20also%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20targeting%20a%20Microsoft%20site%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Microsoft%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20had%20no%20indication%20of%20any%20attack%20and%20that%20its%20data%20centers%20in%20the%20region%20were%20operating%20as%20normal.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20Google%20nor%20Microsoft's%20data%20centers%20have%20shown%20any%20outages%20in%20the%20region%20this%20week%2C%20according%20to%20their%20service%20pages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Friday%2C%20service%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-web-services-data-center-fire-objects-middle-east-strikes-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edamaged%20Amazon%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20remains%20offline%20or%20heavily%20disrupted.%20The%20company%20has%20recommended%20that%20customers%20%26quot%3Benact%20their%20disaster%20recovery%20plans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outages%20underscored%20how%20dependent%20much%20of%20the%20world's%20technology%20is%20on%20data%20centers.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareem-ceo-comments-employees-focused-pay-work-culture-linkedin-post-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMudassir%20Sheikha%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20Dubai-based%20ride-hailing%20and%20food%20delivery%20app%20Careem%2C%20said%20earlier%20this%20week%20that%20some%20of%20its%20services%20were%20%26quot%3Bimpacted%20by%20an%20external%20AWS%20UAE%20outage%26quot%3B%20and%20had%20since%20been%20restored.%20Various%20banking%20apps%20also%20saw%20disruptions%20throughout%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20pointed%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhealth.aws.amazon.com%2Fhealth%2Fstatus%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAWS%20Service%20Health%20Dashboard%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20latest%20updates.%20A%20Google%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275c6c696-eda9-4135-bb49-3dd2ec41de17%5C%22%3EDefending%20data%20centers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-web-services-data-centers-coronavirus-pandemic-2020-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EData%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20typically%20designed%20to%20be%20resilient%2C%20with%20workloads%20often%20distributed%20across%20different%20regions%20to%20limit%20the%20impact%20of%20a%20single%20location%20being%20knocked%20offline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20the%20AI%20boom%20clashes%20against%20turmoil%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20the%20billions%20of%20dollars%20being%20poured%20into%20data%20centers%20come%20with%20more%20risk%20as%20a%20new%20warfare%20strategy%20emerges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BData%20centers%20have%20become%20the%20new%20infrastructure%20for%20economies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20James%20Lewis%2C%20senior%20advisor%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20think%20about%20how%20people%20are%20going%20to%20build%20infrastructure%2C%20before%20it%20was%20railroads%20and%20steam%20engines.%20Now%20it's%20data%20centers%20and%20fiber%20optics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outages%20experienced%20by%20some%20services%20this%20week%20further%20highlighted%20how%20data%20centers%20could%20be%20considered%20a%20key%20infrastructure%20target%20in%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELewis%20cited%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopen-source-developers-ukraine-russia-war-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERussia-Ukraine%20war%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20another%20recent%20example%20in%20which%20data%20became%20central%20to%20the%20conflict%2C%20as%20Ukraine%20took%20steps%20to%20prevent%20Russia%20from%20accessing%20data%20stored%20on%20the%20country's%20servers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20thing%20that%20has%20changed%20now%20in%20the%20Gulf%20is%20that%20people%20need%20to%20think%20about%20'how%20do%20we%20defend%20them%3F'%26quot%3B%20said%20Lewis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20centers%20emit%20a%20big%20heat%20signature%20that%20makes%20them%20difficult%20to%20hide%2C%20Lewis%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20hide%20them.%20The%20question%20is%2C%20can%20you%20harden%20them%3F%20Can%20you%20defend%20them%3F%20That's%20what%20people%20haven't%20thought%20about%20because%20we%20didn't%20have%20to%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaudi%20Arabia%20is%20moving%20quickly%20to%20expand%20its%20data%20center%20capacity%20and%20position%20itself%20as%20a%20major%20global%20player%20in%20AI.%20The%20country%20last%20year%20launched%20Humain%2C%20a%20new%20company%20designed%20to%20build%20a%20full-stack%20AI%20ecosystem%20from%20data%20centers%20up%20to%20the%20models.%20Humain%20has%20also%20struck%20partnerships%20with%20Nvidia%20and%20AMD%20to%20build%20out%20data%20centers%20with%20their%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20tech%20giants%20are%20pledging%20to%20invest%20more%20in%20the%20region.%20In%20November%2C%20Microsoft%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20have%20invested%20%247.9%20billion%20in%20the%20UAE%20by%202029%2C%20while%20Amazon%20pledged%20more%20than%20%245%20billion%20as%20part%20of%20a%20strategic%20partnership%20with%20Humain%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-centers-iran-strikes-uae-bahrain-tech-military-target-war-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772830845000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab1924d3e2f1aef36a24a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-centers-iran-strikes-uae-bahrain-tech-military-target-war-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Middle%20East%20drone%20attacks%20on%20Amazon%20data%20centers%20during%20the%20Iran%20conflict%20underscore%20the%20vulnerability%20of%20critical%20tech%20infrastructure%20in%20warfare.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hlangley%40businessinsider.com%20(Hugh%20Langley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-centers-iran-strikes-uae-bahrain-tech-military-target-war-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20Bryon%20Noem%20left%20Kristi%20despite%20'humiliation'%20because%20of%20the%20Lewandowski%20controversy%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772830275000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129177635%2Cimgsize-27758.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhy-hasnt-bryon-noem-left-kristi-despite-humiliation-because-of-the-lewandowski-controversy%2Farticleshow%2F129177233.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129177233.cms%5C%22%