ider%20that%20Mazur%2C%20a%20stockpicker%20for%20Citadel's%20Global%20Equities%20unit%20since%20the%20summer%20of%202016%2C%20is%20joining%20Izzy%20Englander's%20Millennium%20as%20a%20senior%20portfolio%20manager.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECitadel%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMillennium%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20person%20close%20to%20Citadel%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20manager%20liquidated%20Mazur's%20portfolio%20earlier%20this%20year%20and%20promoted%20two%20people%20under%20him%20%E2%80%94%20Brad%20Gemberling%20and%20Greg%20Fitter%20%E2%80%94%20to%20portfolio%20manager%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMazur%20is%20based%20out%20of%20Chicago%20and%20spent%20close%20to%2012%20years%20at%20San%20Francisco-headquartered%20Harvest%20Capital%20Strategies%20before%20joining%20Citadel.%20He%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edid%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20several%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20what%20Mazur's%20deal%20from%20Millennium%20will%20pay%20him.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-fund-pay-poaching-relocation-mercenaries-buy-loyalty-millennium-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewar%20for%20investing%20talent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20among%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcitadel-millennium-point72-balyasny-dominance-changed-the-hedge-fund-industry-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebig%20four%3C%2Fa%3E%20multistrategy%20firms%2C%20Millennium%2C%20Citadel%2C%20Point72%2C%20and%20Baylasny%2C%20has%20ramped%20up%20the%20costs%20across%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPMs%20typically%20receive%20guaranteed%20payouts%20in%20their%20contracts%2C%20but%20if%20an%20individual%20a%20firm%20wants%20to%20cut%20instead%20resigns%20and%20joins%20another%20firm%2C%20they%20forfeit%20that%20compensation.%20Often%2C%20the%20firm%20that%20hires%20the%20PM%20will%20take%20into%20account%20the%20compensation%20forfeited%20and%20make%20the%20individual%20whole%20with%20a%20sign-on%20bonus%20or%20another%20form%20of%20payout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMillennium%2C%20which%20has%20more%20than%206%2C600%20employees%20and%20hundreds%20of%20investing%20teams%2C%20continues%20to%20add%20to%20its%20roster.%20The%20firm%20poached%20Goldman%20Sachs'%20cohead%20of%20global%20equities%2C%20Erdit%20Hoxha%2C%20last%20month%20to%20join%20its%20Office%20of%20the%20CIO%2C%20which%20oversees%20its%20legions%20of%20trading%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECitadel's%20Global%20Equities%20unit%2C%20run%20by%20Justin%20Lubell%2C%20lost%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-development-execs-left-citadel-past-year-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20top%20talent%20recruiters%20last%20year%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%20first%2C%20Alex%20Topkins%2C%20and%20then%20Laura%20Sterner.%20Sterner%20had%20only%20been%20at%20the%20firm%20for%20two%20months%2C%20Business%20Insider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcitadel-recruiting-exec-laura-sterner-resigns-leaving-company-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epreviously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20unit%20has%20brought%20on%20fresh%20investing%20talent%20this%20year%2C%20the%20person%20close%20to%20the%20Miami-based%20firm%20said.%20Global%20Equities%20poached%20Spencer%20Washburn%2C%20a%20former%20analyst%20at%20Millennium%2C%20to%20manage%20a%20book.%20His%20LinkedIn%20states%20he%20started%20in%20February%20in%20the%20firm's%20New%20York%20offices%20as%20a%20portfolio%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcitadel-daniel-mazur-joining-millennium-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772828368000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60074b4be3d62500185fd369%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcitadel-daniel-mazur-joining-mill