0clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20I%20look%20at%20pictures%20of%20my%20daughter%20Abbey%20when%20she%20was%203%20or%204.%20She%20was%20just%20so%2C%20so%20cute.%20But%20I%20think%20%E2%80%94%20was%20I%20present%20for%20that%3F%20Did%20I%20enjoy%20that%20time%2C%20or%20was%20I%20too%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fsigns-of-autism-in-adults%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eobsessed%20with%20therapies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20my%20worries%20about%20her%20future%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20normal%20for%20anyone%2C%20especially%20parents%2C%20to%20fret%20about%20the%20future%2C%20but%20for%20parents%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-son-has-cerebral-palsy-public-school-wont-accommodate-him-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ekids%20with%20disabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20those%20worries%20can%20be%20overwhelming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbbey%20is%20now%2027.%20When%20she%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20autism%2025%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20couldn't%20have%20imagined%20that%20Abbey%20would%20be%20running%20two%20small%20businesses%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-shows-movies-streaming-netflix-max-prime-april-4-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eappearing%20on%20reality%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20along%20the%20way%2C%20we%20both%20learned%20to%20think%20outside%20the%20box%2C%20and%20that's%20helped%20Abbey%20grow%20so%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225531f35f-0787-4cf2-b3a2-8774b314238b%5C%22%3EI%20put%20Abbey%20in%20a%20vocational%20program%20in%208th%20grade%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAbbey%20went%20to%20one%20of%20the%20best%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fautistic-son-graduated-high-school-cant-go-to-college-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eschools%20for%20autism%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20had%20moderate%20setbacks%2C%20but%20her%20curriculum%20was%20still%20focused%20on%20academics.%20She%20was%20learning%20what%20typical%20kids%20were%2C%20like%20tectonic%20plates%20and%20world%20history%2C%20just%20at%20a%20slower%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abbey%20Romeo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f669de8408f66718045f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChristine%20Romeo%20moved%20her%20daughter%2C%20Abbey%2C%20to%20a%20program%20that%20would%20teach%20her%20life%20skills.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Christine%20Romeo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20see%20that%20wasn't%20what%20she%20needed.%20It's%20not%20helpful%20to%20learn%20Western%20Civilization%20if%20you%20can't%20remember%20what%20you%20did%20yesterday.%20I%20would%20rather%20Abbey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskills-that-will-pay-off-forever-2016-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efocus%20on%20life%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20could%20help%20her%20cope%20with%20her%20autism%2C%20like%20visual%20clues%20to%20help%20her%20access%20her%20short-term%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Abbey%20was%20in%20eighth%20grade%2C%20I%20switched%20her%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-high-schools-changing-value-of-college-trade-higher-education-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evocational%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20focused%20on%20job%20and%20life%20skills.%20I%20had%20to%20set%20my%20ego%20aside%20and%20do%20what%20was%20right%20for%20Abbey.%20She%20didn't%20need%20a%20high%20school%20diploma%20%E2%80%94%20she%20needed%20skills%20to%20help%20her%20live%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220684e9d3-6769-472e-998a-5951dca75aed%5C%22%3EI%20realized%20as%20a%20parent%20you%20don't%20get%20to%20order%20who%20your%20child%20is%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20moments%20throughout%20Abbey's%20schooling%20when%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20made%20the%20right%20decision.%20One%20time%2C%20the%20teacher%20sent%20me%20a%20picture%20of%20Abbey%20rewiring%20a%20light.%20I%20was%20blown%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20was%20when%20I%20came%20in%20to%20see%20Abbey%20weaving%20in%20the%20textile%20program.%20She%20was%20operating%20this%20big%20machine%20with%20foot%20pedals%20and%20a%20large%20swatch%20of%20fabric%2C%20and%20it%20was%20regulating%20her.%20I%20had%20to%20leave%20the%20room%2C%20because%20I%20was%20crying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Abbey%20and%20her%20brother%2C%20who's%20a%20year%20younger%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20as%20a%20parent%2C%20you%20don't%20always%20get%20what%20you%20order.%20I'm%20determined%20to%20help%20both%20of%20them%20be%20who%20they%20are%20and%20be%20as%20successful%20as%20they're%20meant%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22af2223da-9048-4c1b-bd39-feac8ac21a4e%5C%22%3EEntrepreneurs%20inspired%20me%20to%20not%20take%20no%20for%20an%20answer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAbbey%20excelled%20at%20weaving%2C%20and%20I%20realized%20selling%20her%20creations%20could%20be%20a%20job.%20I%20believe%20it's%20important%20for%20everyone%20to%20have%20a%20sense%20of%20purpose%2C%20and%20Abbey%20had%20expressed%20that%20she%20wanted%20a%20%26quot%3Breal%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spoke%20with%20her%20school%20about%20creating%20a%20program%20to%20allow%20kids%20to%20sell%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feasy-fun-craft-ideas-at-home-childhood-nostalgic%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eart%20and%20crafts%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20teacher%20loved%20the%20idea%2C%20but%20the%20principal%20didn't.%20When%20he%20said%20no%2C%20I%20thought%20about%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20shows%2C%20Shark%20Tank%2C%20and%20how%20entrepreneurs%20don't%20take%20no%20for%20an%20answer.%20I%20was%20determined%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20for%20Abbey%2C%20even%20when%20the%20system%20said%20there%20wasn't%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abbey%20Romeo%20making%20a%20hat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F