Cfigcaption%3Ecaptiontk%3Cp%3EAudrey%20Bruno%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20an%20American%20who%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20a%20Frenchman%2C%20now%20my%20husband%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-to-berlin-differences-after-moving-culture-public-transit-2025-11%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eliving%20abroad%20in%20Berlin%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20start%20of%20our%20relationship%20was%20a%20breeze%2C%20but%20we%20soon%20discovered%20some%20cultural%20differences.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20don't%20always%20agree%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20hosting%20and%20meal%20times%2C%20but%20we%20find%20ways%20to%20compromise.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20from%20New%20York%20to%20Berlin%20as%20a%20single%20woman%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20love%20wasn't%20at%20the%20top%20of%20my%20to-do%20list%2C%20but%20I%20was%20open%20to%20the%20possibility%20%E2%80%94%20and%20aware%20that%20the%20odds%20of%20making%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstanford-student-use-viral-dating-matchmaking-app-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edating-app%20match%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20someone%20of%20another%20nationality%20were%20much%20higher%20than%20if%20I%20had%20stayed%20stateside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20wasn't%20exactly%20surprised%20when%20a%20dashing%20Frenchman%2C%20who'd%20eventually%20become%20my%20husband%2C%20whisked%20me%20off%20my%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20managed%20to%20ignore%20the%20cultural%20divide%20during%20those%20first%20six%20months%20of%20honeymoon-phase%20bliss.%20It%20was%20easy%20since%20he%20was%20fluent%20in%20English%20and%20I%20had%20a%20basic%20knowledge%20of%20French%2C%20but%20the%20longer%20we%20went%20on%2C%20the%20harder%20it%20became%20to%20pretend%20we%20hadn't%20had%20upbringings%20in%20countries%20thousands%20of%20miles%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20lucky%20to%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20common%20interests%20and%20have%20agreed%20on%20our%20major%20values%20since%20day%20one%20%E2%80%94%20but%20we've%20come%20to%20accept%20that%20there%20are%20some%20ways%20I'll%20always%20be%20a%20little%20too%20American%20for%20him%20and%20he%20a%20little%20too%20French%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e635b0f5-0b2c-45a5-936e-f03fab61a400%5C%22%3EWe%20have%20opposite%20approaches%20to%20self-medication%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221113%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20writer%20and%20her%20husband%20posing%20in%20the%20bleachers%20at%20a%20sporting%20event.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a718191fb3fcb42648d2da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22835%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3Ecaptiontk%3Cp%3EAudrey%20Bruno%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-of-five-cant-afford-healthcare-plans-marketplace-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EReliable%20health%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20never%20a%20sure%20thing%20for%20my%20family%20when%20I%20was%20growing%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20meant%20that%20we'd%20often%20treat%20illnesses%20on%20our%20own%20when%20possible%2C%20keeping%20the%20medicine%20cabinet%20stocked%20at%20all%20times%20with%20Costco-sized%20bottles%20of%20every%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Faspirin-vs-tylenol%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eover-the-counter%20painkiller%3C%2Fa%3E%20you%20can%20imagine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20think%20twice%20when%20I%20packed%20my%20suitcase%20with%20several%20bottles%20of%20ibuprofen%2C%20but%20they%20were%20a%20shock%20to%20my%20husband%20the%20first%20time%20I%20took%20one%20out%20in%20front%20of%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20France%2C%20painkillers%20like%20ibuprofen%20and%20acetaminophen%20aren't%20easy%20to%20buy%20in%20bulk%20or%20get%20at%20the%20grocery%20store%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20at%20pharmacies%2C%20you%20can't%20grab%20them%20off%20the%20shelf%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20you%20have%20to%20get%20them%20straight%20from%20the%20pharmacist%2C%20who%20will%20then%20typically%20debrief%20you%20on%20proper%20usage%20and%20dosage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20his%20point%20of%20view%2C%20I%20take%20way%20too%20much%20ibuprofen%20%E2%80%A6%20but%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhow-to-stop-coughing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enatural%20remedies%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20has%20always%20used%20often%20don't%20cut%20it%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20this%20week%2C%20I%20came%20down%20with%20a%20cold%2C%20and%20he%20brought%20me%20a%20homeopathic%20essential-oil%20treatment%20when%20I%20asked%20him%20to%20pick%20up%20medicine.%20I've%20been%20using%20it%20to%20appease%20him%2C%20but%20you%20better%20believe%20I%20also%20sent%20him%20back%20to%20get%20the%20ibuprofen%20I%20really%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22abba888c-5190-4d91-97fb-1c59bf9be684%5C%22%3EMy%20husband's%20French%20dining%20habits%20are%20different%20from%20my%20laid-back%2C%20American%20approach%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20often%20have%20trouble%20aligning%20when%20and%20what%20we%20eat%20because%20of%20our%20different%20appetites%20and%20cultural%20approaches%20to%20dining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20France%2C%20eating%20routines%20tend%20to%20be%20pretty%20rigid.%20Lunch%20happens%20at%20noon%20sharp%2C%20breakfast%20is%20always%20sweet%2C%20and%20the%20only%20time%20of%20day%20most%20people%20snack%20is%20at%204%20p.m.%20for%20their%20%26quot%3Bgo%C3%BBter%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20childhood%20habit%20of%20taking%20a%20sugary%2C%20late-afternoon%20treat%20that%20many%20French%20folks%2C%20including%20my%20husband%2C%20carry%20with%20them%20long%20after%20they've%20left%20the%20schoolyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20approach%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20mirrors%20the%20free-form%20way%20I%20ate%20in%20the%20US.%20Snacks%20are%20always%20on%20hand%2C%20breakfast%20is%20often%20skipped%2C%20and%20dinnertime%20could%20easily%20take%20place%20early%20one%20night%20and%20late%20the%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20of%20us%20has%20been%20able%20to%20fully%20adapt%20to%20the%20other's%20eating%20style%2C%20but%20we%20try%20to%20make%20time%20to%20enjoy%20at%20least%20one%20meal%20together%20a%20day%20%E2%80%94%20usually%20dinner.%20That%20way%2C%20we%20can%20find%20something%20we%20agree%20on%2C%20and%20a%20time%20to%20eat%20it%2C%20and%20get%20what%20we%20both%20want%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229d9b9f85-88a8-461a-ac9c-43e9f8834f91%5C%22%3EWe%20often%20don't%20agree%20on%20how%20or%20when%20to%20share%20our%20personal%20space%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22896%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20writer%20and%20her%20husband%20kissing%20on%20a%20pathway%2C%20with%20a%20green%20landscape%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a7176a1fb3fcb42648d2a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22678%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3Ecaptiontk%3Cp%3EAudrey%20Bruno%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20had%20an%20open-door%20policy%20for%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20and%20welcomed%20the%20opportunity%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretiree-house-sitter-travels-world-renting-house-aribnb-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehire%20a%20housesitter%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20leave%20my%20apartment%20to%20a%20friend%20to%20watch%20my%20cats%20when%20I'm%20out%20of%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20mind%20if%20they%20make%20themselves%20at%20home%20while%20they're%20at%20it%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20that%20means%20sleeping%20in%20my%20bed%20or%20using%20my%20shampoo%20and%20conditioner%20%E2%80%94%20possibly%20because%20I%20grew%20up%20watching%20my%20own%20parents%20always%20offer%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20however%2C%20is%20out%20of%20the%20realm%20of%20possibility%20for%20my%20husband.%20The%20first%20time%20I%20proposed%20such%20an%20idea%20before%20a%20long%20vacation%2C%20he%20shut%20it%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20France%2C%20people%20don't%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20sleep%20in%20our%20own%20beds%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day.%26quot%3B%20Friends%20will%20swing%20by%20to%20feed%20the%20cats%20and%20change%20the%20litter%2C%20but%20that's%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20limit%20to%20how%20long%20he%20feels%20comfortable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhosted-dinner-party-every-saturday-make-friends-parent-lonely-2026-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehosting%20guests%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20we%20%3Cem%3Eare%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20premises%20%E2%80%94%20but%20he's%20learned%20to%20adapt%20to%20longer%20stays%20in%20order%20to%20accommodate%20my%20loved%20ones%20who%20have%20to%20travel%20from%20afar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20first%20met%2C%20the%20longest%20stretch%20he%20could%20tolerate%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-successful-people-spend-long-holiday-weekends-2017-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elong%20weekend%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20we've%20since%20hosted%20my%20California-based%20siblings%20for%20several%20weeks%20with%20no%20complaints%20on%20his%20end%20(OK%2C%20maybe%20just%20a%20few).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20although%20we%20may%20both%20never%20be%20%3Cem%3Etotally%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20board%20with%20each%20other's%20cultural%20quirks%2C%20at%20least%20we%20know%20that%20we'll%20always%20try%20to%20meet%20in%20the%20middle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-married-to-french-man-cultural-differences-meals-etiquette-hosting-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772820121000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.in