es%20says%20the%20sell-off%20has%20created%20good%20discounts%20for%20a%20handful%20of%20stocks.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere%20are%20the%20firm's%20top%20picks%20among%20the%20market's%20AI-impacted%20names.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJefferies%20says%20the%20AI%20fear%20trade%20has%20pushed%20a%20handful%20of%20solid%20stock%20picks%20into%20the%20%26quot%3Bdiscount%20bin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStocks%20in%20a%20range%20of%20industries%20have%20been%20hit%20by%20worries%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-job-losses-wall-street-strategist-citrini-research-citadel-securities-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etech-fueled%20disruptions%20to%20businesses%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Jefferies%2C%20like%20many%20top%20Wall%20Street%20firms%2C%20says%20that%20while%20AI%20will%20disrupt%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20investors'%20worries%20have%20fueled%20indiscriminate%20selling%2C%20taking%20down%20some%20shares%20that%20are%20still%20a%20good%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20it%20remains%20early%20days%20in%20terms%20of%20AI%20development%20%26amp%3B%20deployments%2C%20and%20there%20will%20certainly%20be%20%5Blongterm%5D%20casualties%2C%20we%20believe%20some%20stocks%20have%20been%20unjustly%20accused%20in%20the%20court%20of%20investor%20opinion%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20beaten-down%20stocks%20the%20firm%20says%20are%20a%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220bfd8a4a-763a-4430-ac1c-12a41df95e42%5C%22%3ESallie%20Mae%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETicker%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fslm-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESLM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYear-to-date%20move%3A%20-30%25%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJefferies'%20bullish%20outlook%20for%20the%20consumer%20finance%20name%20revolves%20around%20the%20impact%20of%20AI%20on%20the%20labor%20market.%20The%20evolving%20tech%20threatens%20entry-level%20roles%2C%20a%20major%20risk%20for%20recent%20college%20graduates%20looking%20to%20secure%20a%20job%20post-graduation%2C%20reshaping%20education%20priorities%20and%20the%20student%20loan%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20affects%20SLM%20directly%20in%20terms%20of%20credit%20performance%20if%20recent%20grads%20fail%20to%20land%20a%20job%20and%20are%20unable%20to%20pay%20back%20their%20student%20loans%2C%20and%20originations%20volume%20down%20the%20line%2C%20if%20the%20value%20of%20investing%20in%20a%20college%20degree%20diminishes%20and%20potentially%20fewer%20people%20enroll%20in%20undergraduate%20or%20graduate%20programs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%2C%20though%2C%20that%20they%20see%20upside%20potential%20%26quot%3Bas%20structural%20shifts%20and%20specializations%20occur%20in%20education%20program%20offering.%20We%20also%20see%20potential%20for%20a%20higher%20revaluation%20as%20fee%20income%20grows%20as%20a%20percentage%20of%20total%20revenues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fe7e0ce5-afb4-46cf-99ae-a00a5390fcdb%5C%22%3ELincoln%20National%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETicker%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Flnc-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELNC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYear-to-date%20move%3A%20-26%25%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELincoln%20National%2C%20an%20insurance%20company%2C%20has%20sold%20off%20on%20investor%20fears%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-job-losses-dot-com-bubble-internet-economy-morgan-stanley-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20disruption%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Jefferies%20said%20AI%20worries%20are%20overblown.%20Insurance%2C%20along%20with%20wealth%20management%20and%20real%20estate%20stocks%2C%20were%20among%20the%20shares%20taken%20down%20last%20month%20by%20a%20series%20of%20updates%20to%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Jefferies%20analysts%20expect%20AI%20will%20augment%20the%20role%20of%20financial%20advisors%2C%