ighlighted%20the%20tech%20giant's%20dominance%20in%20enterprise%20software%20and%20the%20benefits%20of%20AI%20integration%20with%20Anthropic%20and%20OpenAI%20into%20its%20products%20as%20positive%20signals%20for%20a%20path%20to%20AI%20monetization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2200a714ee-5171-4072-ad50-bf817c396fe9%5C%22%3ECapital%20One%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETicker%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fcof-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECOF%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYear-to-date%20move%3A%20-23%25%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJefferies%20named%20Capital%20One%20as%20a%20top%20stock%20pick%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20%26quot%3Bpure%26quot%3B%20AI%E2%80%91driven%20retail%20bank%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20the%20company's%20Discover%20merger%20supports%20their%20view.%20They%20said%20that%20Capital%20One%20has%20done%20a%20good%20job%20positioning%20itself%20as%20a%20tech%20company%20that%20does%20banking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20AI%20disruption%20front%2C%20COF%20has%20always%20been%20widely%20regarded%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20AI%E2%80%91mature%20financial%20institutions%20in%20the%20US%2C%20using%20proprietary%20AI%20and%20%5Bmachine%20learning'%5D%20at%20scale%20across%20customer-facing%20products%2C%20risk%20management%20and%20internal%20operations.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220373aed4-980f-486e-b1e4-fae42377d55e%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETicker%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fmeta-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMETA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYear-to-date%20move%3A%20-3%25%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20clear%20AI%20beneficiary%2C%26quot%3B%20Jefferies%20said%2C%20explaining%20that%20%26quot%3Blarge%E2%80%91scale%20AI%20investments%20already%20driving%20measurable%20gains%20across%20engagement%20and%20monetization%20and%20setting%20up%20a%20reacceleration%20in%20growth%20in%202026.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%