nd%20loneliness%20across%20this%20tracklist%20%E2%80%94%20I%20particularly%20like%20%26quot%3BThe%20Waiting%20Game%26quot%3B%20as%20an%20allegory%20for%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-most-rejected-generation-college-careers-jobs-dating-ghosting-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eendless%20parade%20of%20rejections%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20flings%20%E2%80%94%20but%20Styles%20never%20introspects%20for%20long.%20At%20times%2C%20he%20even%20seems%20to%20insist%20that%20he%20has%20nothing%20outstanding%20to%20say%2C%20no%20reason%20for%20us%20to%20listen%20to%20this%20music%20over%20anything%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOh%2C%20what%20a%20gift%20it%20is%20to%20be%20noticed%20%2F%20But%20it's%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Styles%20sings%20in%20%26quot%3BPaint%20By%20Numbers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20album's%20worst%20misfire.%20This%20lyric%20is%20also%20printed%20inside%20its%20physical%20vinyl%20gatefolds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStyles%20is%20nothing%20if%20not%20true%20to%20his%20word%3B%20the%20narrator%20of%20these%20songs%20wants%20to%20melt%20into%20the%20music%2C%20to%20be%20lost%20in%20a%20swirl%20of%20limbs%20and%20synths%20on%20a%20dancefloor.%20He%20does%20not%20wish%20to%20stand%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crowd-pleasing%2010th%20track%2C%20%26quot%3BDance%20No%20More%2C%26quot%3B%20presents%20a%20kind%20of%20thesis%20for%20the%20album.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMove%20it%20side%20to%20side%20%2F%20With%20your%20hands%20up%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20Styles%20sings.%20%26quot%3BKeep%20your%20customer%20satisfied%20%2F%20And%20live%20your%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20not%20be%20ingenious%20or%20especially%20thrilling%2C%20but%20it%20is%20an%20effective%20sales%20strategy.%20Styles%20is%20an%20expert%20in%20non-specific%2C%20unserious%2C%20broadly%20enjoyable%20pop%20music%2C%20and%20it's%20made%20him%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20Why%20stop%20now%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20