ttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-engineers-getting-crushed-by-ai-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EComputer%20programmers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20customer%20service%20representatives%2C%20data%20entry%20keyers%2C%20medical%20record%20specialists%2C%20and%20market%20research%20analysts%20and%20marketing%20specialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20has%20yet%20to%20significantly%20affect%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20for%20workers%20in%20these%20highly%20exposed%20professions%2C%20economists%20Maxim%20Massenkoff%20and%20Peter%20McCrory%20wrote.%20The%20pair%20said%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bsuggestive%20evidence%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20hiring%20of%20young%20workers%20in%20those%20fields%20has%20slowed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOur%20measure%2C%20%26quot%3Bobserved%20exposure%2C%26quot%3B%20compares%20the%20tasks%20LLMs%20are%20theoretically%20capable%20of%20to%20the%20tasks%20people%20actually%20use%20Claude%20for%20at%20work.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWe%20find%20that%20actual%20usage%20is%20far%20from%20reaching%20theoretical%20capability.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FcnbkRNMu26%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FcnbkRNMu26%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Peter%20McCrory%20(%40PeterMcCrory)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPeterMcCrory%2Fstatus%2F2029716715916198006%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%206%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EMassenkoff%20and%20McCrory%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Ffiles%2F4zrzovbb%2Fwebsite%2F3f7fd9d552e66269bdb108e207c5d80531d04b8b.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20there%20are%20a%20number%20of%20tasks%20and%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20whole%20jobs%20that%20AI%20can't%20do%2C%20such%20as%20making%20legal%20arguments%20in%20a%20courtroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20tasks%2C%20of%20course%2C%20remain%20beyond%20AI's%20reach%E2%80%94from%20physical%20agricultural%20work%20like%20pruning%20trees%20and%20operating%20farm%20machinery%20to%20legal%20tasks%20like%20representing%20clients%20in%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20pair%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20core%20of%20Massenkoff%20and%20McCrory's%20paper%20proposes%20a%20new%20way%20to%20measure%20AI%20displacement%20risk%20that%20combines%20real-world%20data%20on%20Claude%20usage%20with%20other%20factors%2C%20including%20tasks%20that%20are%20theoretically%20possible%20for%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20has%20been%20publishing%20real-world%20data%20on%20Claude%20usage%20for%20every%20state%20and%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20through%20their%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.anthropic.com%2Feconomic-index%23us-usage%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnthropic%20Economic%20Index.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20doing%20so%2C%20the%20pair%20said%20that%20they%20hope%20to%20pinpoint%20economic%20disruption%20more%20reliably%20in%20real%20time%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20to%20%26quot%3Bhelp%20identify%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20jobs%20before%20displacement%20is%20visible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20approach%20won't%20capture%20every%20channel%20through%20which%20AI%20could%20reshape%20the%20labor%20market%2C%20but%20by%20laying%20this%20groundwork%20now%2C%20before%20meaningful%20effects%20have%20emerged%2C%20we%20hope%20future%20findings%20will%20more%20reliably%20identify%20economic%20disruption%20than%20post-hoc%20analyses%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20measure%2C%20which%20they%20call%20Observed%20Exposure%2C%20shows%20just%20how%20far%20LLMs%20have%20to%20go%20to%20disrupt%20specific%20job%20tasks%20that%20AI%20could%20theoretically%20replace%20or%20augment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20instance%2C%20Claude%20currently%20covers%20just%2033%25%20of%20all%20tasks%20in%20the%20Computer%20%26amp%3B%20Math%20category%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fb49fc39-e1af-4bcd-8f14-4d92917bff19%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDario%20Amodei%20has%20warned%20about%20the%20future%20of%20white-collar%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdario-amodei%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDario%20Amodei%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20repeatedly%20sounded%20the%20alarm%20about%20AI%20job%20displacement.%20He%20has%20said%20that%20AI%20could%20replace%20up%20to%20half%20of%20all%20entry-level%20white-collar%20jobs%20in%20the%20next%20one%20to%20five%20years.%20Amodei%20has%20stuck%20by%20his%20views%20even%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwill-ai-replace-take-over-create-jobs-debate-tech-leaders-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eothers%20in%20the%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20have%20questioned%20his%20outlook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMassenkoff%20and%20McCrory's%20findings%20dovetail%20with%20a%20growing%20consensus%20that%20AI%20could%20eliminate%20most%20entry-level%20software%20engineering%20jobs.%20One%20of%20the%20biggest%20uses%20for%20Anthropic's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-outages-anthropic-ai-software-engineers-developers-coding-dependance-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaude%20is%20coding.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoris%20Cherny%2C%20creator%20of%20Claude%20Code%2C%20recently%20said%20he%20expects%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-code-founder-ai-impacts-software-engineer-role-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etitle%20of%20software%20engineer%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20start%20to%20%26quot%3Bgo%20away%26quot%3B%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ExAI%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20last%20year%20that%20%26quot%3Banything%20that%20is%20physically%20moving%20atoms%26quot%3B%20will%20outlast%20AI%20disruption%20longer.%20The%20Anthropic%20economists%20found%20that%20the%20least%20exposed%20professions%20include%20cooks%2C%20motorcycle%20mechanics%2C%20lifeguards%2C%20bartenders%2C%20and%20dishwashers%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20sweeping%20predictions%20of%20AI%20job%20disruption%20haven't%20always%20aged%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeoffrey%20Hinton%2C%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3BGodfather%20of%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20in%202016%20that%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20should%20stop%20training%20radiologists%20now%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20within%20five%20years%20AI%20would%20surpass%20humans%20in%20the%20field.%20A%20decade%20later%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fradiology-embraces-generative-ai-to-streamline-productivity-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eradiologists%20remain%20in%20demand%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Hinton%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20in%202025%20that%20his%20prediction%20was%20too%20broad%20and%20that%20the%20timing%20was%20off%2C%20even%20as%20he%20was%20correct%20about%20the%20direction%20of%20AI%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20disruption%20also%20won't%20affect%20everyone%20the%20same%20way%2C%20the%20Anthropic%20economists%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20US%20Census%20Bureau%20data%20from%20the%20three%20months%20before%20ChatGPT's%20release%2C%20the%20economists%20found%20that%20%26quot%3BWorkers%20in%20the%20most%20exposed%20professions%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20older%2C%20female%2C%20more%20educated%2C%20and%20higher-paid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-is-tracking-the-jobs-most-exposed-to-ai-disruption-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772816004000%2