eat-on-companys-data-centre-plans-says-we-see-a-huge%2Farticleshow%2F129166569.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20gas%20prices%20climb%20to%20the%20highest%20point%20in%20Trump's%20second%20term.%20He%20says%2C%20'If%20they%20rise%2C%20they%20rise.'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20in%20a%20white%20jacket%20and%20black%20pants%20replaces%20the%20gas%20pump%20at%20the%20station.%20She%20is%20standing%20next%20to%20a%20gold%20Chevy%20Malibu%20sedan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aadf64d3e2f1aef36a1ca8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGas%20prices%20have%20risen%20sharply%20since%20the%20military%20conflict%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Iran%20began.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Raedle%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20average%20price%20for%20a%20gallon%20of%20regular%20gas%20in%20the%20US%20rose%20to%20%243.32%20on%20Friday%2C%20according%20to%20AAA.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat's%20an%2011.4%25%20rise%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20highest%20retail%20price%20of%20President%20Trump's%20second%20term.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBrent%20crude%20prices%2C%20the%20global%20benchmark%20for%20oil%2C%20rose%20to%20%2491%20a%20barrel%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faverage-gas-price-largest-single-day-jump-iran-attacks-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGas%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20continued%20their%20ascent%20on%20Friday%20as%20the%20escalating%20conflict%20with%20Iran%20sends%20shockwaves%20through%20global%20energy%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20average%20price%20for%20a%20gallon%20of%20regular%20gasoline%20climbed%20to%20%243.32%20on%20Friday%2C%20according%20to%20AAA%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20an%2011.4%25%20increase%20from%20last%20week's%20price%20and%20the%20highest%20level%20since%20A