%5C%22%3Eattacked%20a%20tanker%20passing%20through%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20waterway%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20disruption%20there%20could%20quickly%20drive%20oil%20prices%20higher%20%E2%80%94%20and%20those%20moves%20would%20show%20up%20at%20the%20pump%20within%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIran%20has%20also%20targeted%20regional%20energy%20infrastructure%2C%20including%20facilities%20tied%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fqatarenergy-pauses-production-after-iranian-strikes-hit-energy-facilities-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EQatar's%20massive%20liquefied%20natural%20gas%3C%2Fa%3E%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20downplayed%20the%20retail%20price%20increase%20when%20asked%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fenergy%2Ftrump-rising-gas-prices-during-iran-operation-if-they-rise-they-rise-2026-03-05%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20rising%20fuel%20costs%20this%20week%2C%20saying%20he%20does%20not%20%26quot%3Bhave%20any%20concern%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey'll%20drop%20very%20rapidly%20when%20this%20is%20over%2C%20and%20if%20they%20rise%2C%20they%20rise%2C%20but%20this%20is%20far%20more%20important%20than%20having%20gasoline%20prices%20go%20up%20a%20little%20bit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20said%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-us-oil-price-stock-market-energy-iran-commoditiy-war-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20Navy%20will%20escort%20tankers%3C%2Fa%3E%20passing%20through%20the%20Strait.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetail%20analysts%20warn%20that%20the%20impact%20of%20higher%20energy%20prices%20could%20extend%20beyond%20drivers.%20Higher%20fuel%20costs%20raise%20shipping%20and%20distribution%20expenses%20for%20businesses%20and%20can%20weigh%20on%20consumer%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20oil%20prices%20rise%2C%20gas%20prices%20follow%2C%26quot%3B%20Carol%20Spieckerman%2C%20an%20independent%20retail%20analyst%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20with%20the%20administration%20promising%20lower%20prices%20and%20consumers%20laser-focused%20on%20the%20pump%2C%20this%20metric%20has%20been%20given%20arguably%20more%20political%20and%20psychological%20energy%20than%20any%20other%20economic%20variable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20the%20impact%20will%20stretch%20far%20beyond%20the%20gas%20station.%20Higher%20fuel%20costs%20can%20push%20up%20travel%2C%20delivery%2C%20and%20retail%20prices%20%E2%80%94%20including%20goods%20made%20with%20petroleum-based%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ripple%20effects%20of%20fuel%20prices%20are%20far-reaching%20and%20underestimated%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20compounding%20effect%20that%20touches%20nearly%20every%20corner%20of%20retail.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-gas-prices-climb-highest-trumps-term-oil-iran-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772814521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aadf741fb3fcb426490a9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-gas-prices-climb-highest-trumps-term-oil-iran-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20average%20American%20paid%20%243.32%20for%20a%20gallon%20of%20regular%20gas%20on%20Friday%2C%20according%20to%20AAA.%20That's%20the%20highest%20since%20August%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bshimkus%40insider.com%20(Ben%20Shimkus)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-gas-prices-climb-highest-trumps-term-oil-iran-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20is%20HMS%20Dragon%20taking%20so%20long%20to%20get%20to%20Cyprus%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A17