%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nobel%20economist%20Paul%20Krugman%20said%20this%20surging%20energy%20price%20should%20'terrify%20Republicans'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Paul%20Krugman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699ef0a250f42603b0f8dc42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPaul%20Krugman.%3Cp%3EGene%20Medi%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPaul%20Krugman%20said%20a%20spike%20in%20a%20key%20energy%20benchmark%20should%20%26quot%3Bterrify%20Republicans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Nobel-winning%20economist%20pointed%20to%20a%20sharp%20price%20rise%20for%20futures%20on%20wholesale%20gasoline.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Trump's%20pledge%20to%20bring%20down%20prices%20is%20set%20to%20be%20a%20key%20theme%20in%20the%20US%20midterm%20elections.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Krugman%20says%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-iran-conflict-economic-impact-finance-economy-investing-krugman-zandi-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS-Iran%20conflict%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20causing%20a%20key%20energy%20price%20to%20spike%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20bad%20news%20for%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20given%20he's%20under%20pressure%20to%20bring%20down%20living%20costs%20and%20tackle%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-biggest-economic-mistake-prices-affordability-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaffordability%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20people%20talking%20about%20how%20gasoline%20prices%20at%20the%20pump%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faverage-gas-price-largest-single-day-jump-iran-attacks-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ealready%20jumped%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Krugman%20wrote%20in%20a%20BlueSky%20post%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20what%20should%20really%20terrify%20Republicans%20is%20RBOB%20%E2%80%94%20the%20futures%20price%20on%20wholesale%20gasoline.%20This%20is%20up%2075%20cents%20a%20gallon%20since%20its%20low%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fembed.bsky.app%2Fstatic%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-bluesky-cid%3D%5C%22bafyreigxp4nd5yqtfdi5xkvxxgt7vybbldrjkbvpxeqg25m6kieahdejgy%5C%22%20data-bluesky-embed-color-mode%3D%5C%22system%5C%22%20data-bluesky-uri%3D%5C%22at%3A%2F%2Fdid%3Aplc%3Avl7iw2awdpm72srjve3f4fj2%2Fapp.bsky.feed.post%2F3mgaitcnf4k2c%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMany%20people%20talking%20about%20how%20gasoline%20prices%20at%20the%20pump%20have%20already%20jumped.%20But%20what%20should%20really%20terrify%20Republicans%20is%20RBOB%20%E2%80%94%20the%20futures%20price%20on%20wholesale%20gasoline.%20This%20is%20up%2075%20cents%20a%20gallon%20since%20its%20low%20earlier%20this%20year.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsky.app%2Fprofile%2Fdid%3Aplc%3Avl7iw2awdpm72srjve3f4fj2%2Fpost%2F3mgaitcnf4k2c%3Fref_src%3Dembed%5C%22%3E%5Bimage%20or%20embed%5D%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Paul%20Krugman%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsky.app%2Fprofile%2Fdid%3Aplc%3Avl7iw2awdpm72srjve3f4fj2%3Fref_src%3Dembed%5C%22%3E%40pkrugman.bsky.social%3C%2Fa%3E)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsky.app%2Fprofile%2Fdid%3Aplc%3Avl7iw2awdpm72srjve3f4fj2%2Fpost%2F3mgaitcnf4k2c%3Fref_src%3Dembed%5C%22%3EMarch%204%2C%202026%20at%202%3A33%20PM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Frbob-gasoline%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGasoline%20RBOB%20April%20futures%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20surged%20from%20about%20%241.70%20a%20gallon%20at%20the%20start%20of%20this%20year%20to%20around%20%242.70%20on%20Friday%2C%20a%20roughly%2060%25%20rise%20in%20just%20over%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERBOB%20is%20a%20key%20refined%20byproduct%20of%20crude%20oil.%20The%20soaring%20price%20of%20its%20futures%20suggests%20prices%20at%20the%20pump%20will%20rise%20by%20a%20similar%20magnitude%2C%20Krugman%20said%20in%20a%20YouTube%20video%20that%20expanded%20on%20his%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20pledge%20to%20bring%20down%20prices%20as%20president%20is%20set%20to%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fk-shaped-economy-wealth-gap-gary-cohn-trump-economic-advisor-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ekey%20talking%20point%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20this%20year's%20midterm%20elections.%20Krugman's%20point%20is%20that%20Republicans%20might%20be%20blamed%20for%20elevated%20gas%20prices%20if%20they're%20seen%20as%20a%20result%20of%20Trump's%20bombing%20campaign%20against%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaul-krugman-iran-conflict-stock-market-economic-outlook-oil-price-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESubstack%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20winner%20of%20the%20Nobel%20Memorial%20Prize%20in%20Economic%20Sciences%20and%20former%20New%20York%20Times%20columnist%20predicted%20prolonged%20disruption%20to%20energy%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20cited%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20clear%20ending%20to%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20between%20Iran%20and%20the%20US%20and%20Israel%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%20being%20a%20key%20global%20energy%20supplier%2C%20and%20likely%20weekslong%20disruption%20in%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20a%20key%20shipping%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20Krugman%20said%20the%20current%20supply%20shock%20didn't%20seem%20as%20severe%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-oil-crisis-in-the-1970s-2012-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eenergy%20crisis%20of%20the%201970s%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20largely%20because%20the%20world%20is%20less%20dependent%20on%20oil%20now%20than%2050%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20economist%20projected%20that%20the%20roughly%20%2415%20rise%20in%20the%20price%20of%20a%20barrel%20of%20oil%20so%20far%20would%20cause%20a%200.3%20percentage-point%20increase%20in%20Americans'%20overall%20cost%20of%20living.%20A%20%2450%20spike%20from%20pre-bombing%20levels%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-iran-oil-prices-inflation-outlook-trump-affordability-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eraise%20consumer%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20around%201%25%2C%20he%20estimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Krugman%20underscored%20that%20the%20economy%20is%20already%20being%20squeezed%20by%20tariffs%20and%20%26quot%3Bdraconian%20anti-immigrant%20policies%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20also%20being%20threatened%20by%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-michael-burry-big-short-nvidia-palantir-ai-bubble-stocks-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epotential%20AI%20bubble%20bursting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20AI-driven%20job%20losses%2C%20and%20signs%20of%20financial%20instability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20we've%20added%20a%20fresh%20level%20of%20massive%20uncertainty%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20many%20stresses%20on%20our%20economy%2C%20and%20this%20could%20be%20the%20straw%20that%20breaks%20the%20camel's%20back%20%E2%80%94%20a%20straw%20that%20becomes%20heavier%20the%20longer%20the%20war%20goes%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20other%20market%20commentators%20have%20flagged%20the%20rising%20price%20of%20RBOB%20futures%20as%20worrying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHormuz%20is%20closed%2C%20with%20no%20solution%20in%20sight%2C%26quot%3B%20Marko%20Kolanovic%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20market%20strategist%20at%20JPMorgan%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20Thursday%20post%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BGasoline%20(RBOB)%20is%20up%2050%25%20YTD.%20And%20equity%20investors%20are%20just%20preoccupied%20with%20software%20vs.%20semis%20game%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRBOB%20%242.71..%20a%2052wk%20high..%20tack%20on%2095%20cents%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20expected%20national%20pump%20average..%2C%26quot%3B%20financial%20writer%20Mike%20Zaccardi%20posted%20to%20X%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERBOB%20%242.71..%20a%2052wk%20high..%20tack%20on%2095%20cents%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20expected%20national%20pump%20average..%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F74sCYxnnNw%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F74sCYxnnNw%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mike%20Zaccardi%2C%20CFA%2C%20CMT%20%F0%9F%8D%96%20(%40MikeZaccardi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMikeZaccardi%2Fstatus%2F2029895063732404538%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%206%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaul-krugman-energy-gas-price-iran-spike-trump-affordability-midterms-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772813579000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a96e701fb3fcb42648f43b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaul-krugman-energy-gas-price-iran-spike-trump-affordability-midterms-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Paul%20Krugman%20said%20a%20spike%20in%20the%20price%20of%20wholesale%20gasoline%20futures%20is%20bad%20news%20for%20President%20Trump%20and%20his%20party%20ahead%20of%20the%20midterm%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmohamed%40businessinsider.com%20(Theron%20Mohamed)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaul-krugman-energy-gas-pr